text: Lel () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Verkhnestaritskoye Rural Settlement, Gaynsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 163 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 45 km north from Verkhnyaya Staritsa. == References == Category:Rural localities in Gaynsky District
title: Lel (settlement)
